&lt;p&gt;The Chief of Staff serves as the Chairman’s strategic partner, operational anchor, and execution engine across a wide portfolio of businesses, investments, and new ventures. This role supports the Chairman’s highest priorities by driving clarity, velocity, and alignment across projects, ensuring that vision is consistently translated into action. The Chief of Staff will streamline decision-making, manage complex multi-stakeholder initiatives, oversee information flow, and proactively remove barriers so the Chairman can operate at maximum impact. This position also includes managing select personal scheduling, meetings, and commitments to protect the Chairman’s time and enable focus.&lt;/p&gt;
